In order to delete a event, the user will have to send his token, and the id of the event to delete

If any user tries to delete a event that does not belong to him, a 401 code will be returned, denying the execution of said action.

If the requested event is not found, it will return 404 code

```response:200
{
 "message":"event deleted succesfull"
}
```

```response:401
{
 "error":"Check token"
}
```

```response:404
{
 "error":"event not found"
}
```

