```

To delete the data of an activity you need the token and the user id, if the identifier is not recognized a 401 error message will be returned.

```response:401
  {
    "message": "Unauthorized"
  }
```

To delete it you need the token and the user id, if both are valid the message 200 is returned.

```response:200
  {
    "message": "An activity has been deleted"
  }
```

In order to delete a board, the user will have to send his token, and the id of the board to delete

**The board and all its task will be deleted as well**

If any user tries to delete a board that does not belong to him, a 401 code will be returned, denying the execution of said action.

If the requested task is not found, it will return 404 code

```response:200
{
 "message":"deleted Board succesfull" 
}
```

```response:401
{
 "error":"Check token"
}
```

```response:404
{
 "error":"board not found"
}
```

